chown user1 file/dir
• Changes the owner (user) of the file or directory to user1.
• The group ownership remains unchanged.

chgrp group1 filename/dir
• Changes the group ownership of the file or directory to group1.
• The user (owner) remains unchanged.

chown user1:group1 filename/dir
• Changes both the owner and the group of the file or directory.
• user1 becomes the owner and group1 becomes the group.
